      â†’â€¦
   169â†’## File format
   171â†’The format is not formally specified and still improves over time. That being
   172â†’said, `.env` files should mostly look like Bash files. Reading from FIFOs (named
   173â†’pipes) on Unix systems is also supported.
   174â†’
